{"tid":464401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嶺大女生中電騙陷阱　損失近2萬 (10:24)","createTime":"2017-11-10T13:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T04:20:55.000Z","uid":53026,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"25d6dbce14d3df2cf14dab63627da8f0d559110f","tid":464401,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:15:19.000Z","msg":"嶺大女生中電騙陷阱　損失近2萬 (10:24)<br />\n（明報資料圖片）<br />\n圖1之1 - （明報資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n電騙停不了。一名18歲姓<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Xu</span></span></strong>的嶺南大學女學生早前接獲一名不明男子來電，對方聲稱為執法人員，電話其後被轉駁至另一名聲稱為內地執法人員的男子，該名男子指女事主與一宗刑事案件有關，要求她將4.2萬港元存入一個內地銀行戶口，女事主按指示存款1.9萬元後，懷疑受騙，於是報案。警方經初步調查，案件列作「以欺騙手段取得財產」處理，交由屯門警區刑事調查隊第7隊跟進，正追查騙徒下落。"},{"pid":"85fe340f50bfd674296b34d88784d53aba1c1da1","tid":464401,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69fb64f5746541c7cbee60022251dcd63e3f8e3","tid":464401,"uid":60281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:40:39.000Z","msg":"又係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b905f70b8f7a06cddece123dd84b0e76e536ea","tid":464401,"uid":39316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:23:44.000Z","msg":"宜家d電話騙案變左人蝗分辨器<br />\n係人定蝗一呃就分得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f54f8fcdc456acce980254a5cef65a9a327d569","tid":464401,"uid":5056,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:29:46.000Z","msg":"成廿幾歲人咁蠢都有嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實每間大學都應該強制呢班所謂內地生<br />\n每個星期抽兩個鐘重溫警訊<br />\n仲要出埋midterm final 計埋grade先得"},{"pid":"3efcd6dba50ab407946af78a600ad32c79a9a575","tid":464401,"uid":61325,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:47: